[{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/447", "id": 1690109523, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5PdvRA", "number": 447, "title": "Release v0.7.2", "user": {"login": "soywod", "id": 10437171, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDM3MTcx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10437171?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod", "html_url": "https://github.com/soywod", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2023-04-30T22:24:47Z", "updated_at": "2023-04-30T22:51:28Z", "closed_at": "2023-04-30T22:25:23Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/pulls/447", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/447", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/447.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/447.patch", "merged_at": "2023-04-30T22:25:23Z"}, "body": "### Added\r\n\r\n- Added `create` and `delete` folder commands [sourcehut#54].\r\n- Added generated completions and man pages to releases\r\n  [sourcehut#43].\r\n- Added new account config option `sync-folders-strategy` which allows\r\n  to choose a folders synchronization strategy [sourcehut#59]:\r\n  \r\n  - `sync-folders-strategy = \"all\"`: synchronize all existing folders\r\n    for the current account\r\n  - `sync-folders-strategy.include = [\"folder1\", \"folder2\", \u2026]`:\r\n    synchronize only the given folders for the current account\r\n  - `sync-folders-strategy.exclude = [\"folder1\", \"folder2\", \u2026]`:\r\n    synchronizes all folders except the given ones for the current\r\n    account\r\n\r\n  Also added new `account sync` arguments that override the account\r\n  config option:\r\n  \r\n  - `-A|--all-folders`: include all folders to the synchronization.\r\n  - `-F|--include-folder`: include given folders to the\r\n    synchronization. They can be repeated `-F folder1 folder2` or `-F\r\n    folder1 -F folder2`.\r\n  - `-x|--exclude-folder`: exclude given folders from the\r\n    synchronization. They can be repeated `-x folder1 folder2` or `-x\r\n    folder1 -F folder2`.\r\n\r\n- Added cargo features `native-tls` (default), `rustls-tls` and\r\n  `rustls-native-certs`.\r\n\r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n- Made global options truly global, which means they can be used\r\n  everywhere (not only *before* commands but also *after*)\r\n  [sourcehut#60].\r\n- Replaced reply all `-a` argument with `-A` because it conflicted\r\n  with the global option `-a|--account`.\r\n- Replaced `himalaya-lib` by `pimalaya-email`.\r\n- Renamed feature `vendored` to `native-tls-vendored`.\r\n- Removed the `develop` branch, all the development is now done on the\r\n  `master` branch.\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n\r\n- Fixed config deserialization issue with `email-hooks` and\r\n  `email-reading-format`.\r\n- Fixed flags case sensitivity.\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/447/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/444", "id": 1587758093, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5KImCq", "number": 444, "title": "Add Scoop install method", "user": {"login": "rashil2000", "id": 46838874, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ2ODM4ODc0", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/46838874?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000", "html_url": "https://github.com/rashil2000", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rashil2000/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2023-02-16T14:16:50Z", "updated_at": "2023-02-16T15:54:31Z", "closed_at": "2023-02-16T14:45:11Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/pulls/444", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/444", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/444.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/444.patch", "merged_at": "2023-02-16T14:45:11Z"}, "body": "Hi, `himalaya` has been added to Scoop package manager (see https://repology.org/project/himalaya/versions). \r\n\r\nCould you please update the https://pimalaya.org/himalaya/docs/cli/installation.html page as well? Thanks!", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/444/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/443", "id": 1584323011, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5J9Aby", "number": 443, "title": "Release v0.7.1", "user": {"login": "soywod", "id": 10437171, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDM3MTcx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10437171?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod", "html_url": "https://github.com/soywod", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2023-02-14T15:03:07Z", "updated_at": "2023-02-14T16:40:28Z", "closed_at": "2023-02-14T16:40:27Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/pulls/443", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/443", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/443.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/443.patch", "merged_at": "2023-02-14T16:40:27Z"}, "body": "### Added\r\n\r\n- Added command `folders expunge` that deletes all emails marked for\r\n  deletion.\r\n  \r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n- Changed the location of the\r\n  [documentation](https://pimalaya.org/himalaya/docs/).\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n\r\n- Fixed broken links in README.md.\r\n\r\n### Removed\r\n\r\n- Removed the `maildir-backend` cargo feature, it is now included by\r\n  default.\r\n- Removed issues section on GitHub, now issues need to be opened by\r\n  sending an email at\r\n  [~soywod/pimalaya@todo.sr.ht](mailto:~soywod/pimalaya@todo.sr.ht).\r\n\r\n## himalaya-lib v0.6.0\r\n\r\n### Added\r\n\r\n- Added ability to synchronize specific folders only [#37].\r\n- Added `Backend::expunge` function that definitely removes emails\r\n  with the `Deleted` flag.\r\n- Added `Backend::mark_emails_as_deleted` function with a default\r\n  implementation that adds the `Deleted` flag.\r\n\r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n- Changed the way emails are deleted. `Backend::delete_emails` now\r\n  moves the email to the `Trash` folder (or to the corresponding alias\r\n  from the config file). If the target folder is the `Trash` folder,\r\n  it will instead add the `Deleted` flag. Emails are removed with the\r\n  `Backend::expunge` function.\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n\r\n- Fixed `ImapBackend::list_envelopes` pagination.\r\n- Fixed synchronization issues for emails without `Message-ID` header\r\n  by using the `Date` header instead.\r\n- Fixed maildir backend perfs issues by enabling the `mmap` feature of\r\n  the `maildir` crate.\r\n  \r\n### Removed\r\n\r\n- Removed the `maildir-backend` cargo feature, it is now included by\r\n  default.\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/443/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/439", "id": 1515101267, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5Ga3U7", "number": 439, "title": "add issue template", "user": {"login": "soywod", "id": 10437171, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDM3MTcx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10437171?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod", "html_url": "https://github.com/soywod", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2022-12-31T11:44:14Z", "updated_at": "2022-12-31T12:26:28Z", "closed_at": "2022-12-31T12:26:25Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/pulls/439", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/439", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/439.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/439.patch", "merged_at": "2022-12-31T12:26:25Z"}, "body": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/439/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/433", "id": 1498835349, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5FkUIb", "number": 433, "title": "Release v0.7.0", "user": {"login": "soywod", "id": 10437171, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDM3MTcx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10437171?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod", "html_url": "https://github.com/soywod", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/soywod/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2022-12-15T17:38:47Z", "updated_at": "2023-02-08T15:03:46Z", "closed_at": "2023-02-08T15:03:45Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/pulls/433", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/433", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/433.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/433.patch", "merged_at": "2023-02-08T15:03:45Z"}, "body": "### Added\r\n\r\n* Added offline support with the `account sync` command to synchronize\r\n  a backend to a local Maildir backend [#342].\r\n* Added the flag `--disable-cache` to not use the local Maildir\r\n  backend.\r\n* Added the email composer (from its own\r\n  [repository](https://git.sr.ht/~soywod/mime-msg-builder)) [#341].\r\n* Added Musl builds to releases [#356].\r\n* Added `himalaya man` command to generate man page [#419].\r\n\r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n* Made commands `read`, `attachments`, `flags`, `copy`, `move`,\r\n  `delete` accept multiple ids.\r\n* Flipped arguments `ids` and `folder` for commands `copy` and `move`\r\n  in order the folder not to be considered as an id.\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n\r\n* Fixed missing folder aliases [#430].\r\n\r\n### Removed\r\n\r\n* Removed the `-a|--attachment` argument from `write`, `reply` and\r\n  `forward` commands. Instead you can attach documents directly from\r\n  the template using the syntax `<#part\r\n  filename=/path/to/you/document.ext>`.\r\n* Removed the `-e|--encrypt` flag from `write`, `reply` and `forward`\r\n  commands. Instead you can encrypt and sign parts directly from the\r\n  template using the syntax `<#part type=text/plain encrypt=command\r\n  sign=command>Hello!<#/part>`.\r\n* Removed the `-l|--log-level` option, use instead the `RUST_LOG`\r\n  environment variable (see the\r\n  [wiki](https://github.com/soywod/himalaya/wiki/Tips:debug-and-logs))\r\n\r\n## himalaya-lib `v0.5.0`\r\n\r\n### Added\r\n\r\n* Made backend functions accept a vector of id instead of a single id\r\n  [#20].\r\n* Added function `Backend::purge_folder` that removes all emails\r\n  inside a folder.\r\n* Added new `Backend` functions using the internal id:\r\n  * `get_envelope_internal`: gets an envelope by its internal id\r\n  * `add_email_internal`: adds an email and returns its internal id\r\n  * `get_emails_internal`: gets emails by their internal id\r\n  * `copy_emails_internal`: copies emails by their internal id\r\n  * `move_emails_internal`: copies emails by their internal id\r\n  * `delete_emails_internal`: copies emails by their internal id\r\n  * `add_flags_internal`: adds emails flags by their internal id\r\n  * `set_flags_internal`: set emails flags by their internal id\r\n  * `remove_flags_internal`: removes emails flags by their internal id\r\n* Added emails synchronization feature. Backends that implement the\r\n  `ThreadSafeBackend` trait inherit the `sync` function that\r\n  synchronizes all folders and emails with a local `Maildir` instance.\r\n* Added `Backend::sync` function and link `ThreadSafeBackend::sync` to\r\n  it for the IMAP and the Maildir backends.\r\n* Added the ability to URL encode Maildir folders (in order to fix\r\n  path collisions, for eg `[Gmail]/Sent`). Also added a\r\n  `MaildirBackendBuilder` to facilitate the usage of the\r\n  `url_encoded_folders` option.\r\n* Added a process lock for `ThreadSafeBackend::sync`, this way only\r\n  one synchronization can be performed at a time (for a same account).\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n\r\n* Used native IMAP commands `copy` and `mv`.\r\n* Fixed maildir date envelope parsing.\r\n* Fixed inline attachments not collected.\r\n\r\n### Changed\r\n\r\n* Improved `Backend` method names. Also replaced the `self mut` by a\r\n  `RefCell`.\r\n* Simplified the `Email` struct: there is no custom implementation\r\n  with custom fields. Now, the `Email` struct is just a wrapper around\r\n  `mailparse::ParsedMail`.\r\n* Improved `Flag` structures.\r\n* Changed `Backend` trait functions due to [#20]:\r\n  * `list_envelope` => `list_envelopes`\r\n  * `search_envelope` => `search_envelopes`\r\n  * `get_email` => `get_emails`, takes now `ids: Vec<&str>` and\r\n    returns an `Emails` structure instead of an `Email`)\r\n  * `copy_email` => `copy_emails`, takes now `ids: Vec<&str>`.\r\n  * `move_email` => `move_emails`, takes now `ids: Vec<&str>`.\r\n  * `delete_email` => `delete_emails`, takes now `ids: Vec<&str>`.\r\n  * `add_flags` takes now `ids: Vec<&str>` and `flags: &Flags`.\r\n  * `set_flags` takes now `ids: Vec<&str>` and `flags: &Flags`.\r\n  * `remove_flags` takes now `ids: Vec<&str>` and `flags: &Flags`.\r\n\r\n### Removed\r\n\r\n* The `email::Tpl` structure moved to its [own\r\n  repository](https://git.sr.ht/~soywod/mime-msg-builder).\r\n* Encryption and signed moved with the `email::Tpl` in its own\r\n  repository.\r\n\r\n## Pending issues\r\n\r\n* [x] Waiting for a new release from https://github.com/jonhoo/rust-imap/issues/220.\r\n* [x] Waiting for a new release from https://github.com/zesterer/chumsky/discussions/224#discussioncomment-4373295\r\n* [x] Waiting for an answer on decrypting and verifying parts https://github.com/staktrace/mailparse/issues/112", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/433/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/432", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/432/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/432/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pimalaya/himalaya/issues/432/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pimalaya/himalaya/pull/432", "id": 1498023048, "node_id": "PR_kwDOE1A8Ec5FhitJ", "number": 432, "title": "Configuration wizard", "user": {"login": "kmaasrud", "id": 54394333, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU0Mzk0MzMz", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/54394333?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmaasrud", "html_u